"    [launch_online_dp.py](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/examples/external_online_dp/launch_online_dp.py)"
msgstr ""
"1. `launch_online_dp.py`用于启动外部dp vllm服务器。\n"
"    [launch_online_dp.py](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/examples/external_online_dp/launch_online_dp.py)"

msgid "Parameter descriptions:"
msgstr "参数说明："

msgid ""
"|Parameter|Type|Required|Default|Description|\n"
"    |---------|----|--------|-------|-----------|\n"
"    |`--dp-size`|int|Yes|-|Data parallel size (total number of DP ranks across all nodes).|\n"
"    |`--tp-size`|int|No|1|Tensor parallel size within each DP rank.|\n"
"    |`--dp-size-local`|int|No|(same as `--dp-size`)|Number of DP ranks on the current node. If not set, defaults to `--dp-size`.|\n"
"    |`--dp-rank-start`|int|No|0|Starting rank offset for data parallel ranks on this node.|\n"
"    |`--dp-address`|str|Yes|-|IP address of the data parallel master node (node 0).|\n"
"    |`--dp-rpc-port`|str|No|12345|RPC port for data parallel master communication.|\n"
"    |`--vllm-start-port`|int|No|9000|Starting port for each vLLM engine instance on this node. Each DP rank's engine port = `vllm_start_port` + local rank index.|"
msgstr ""
